isocline.reflow

Class PlanImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • isocline.reflow.PlanImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Activity, Plan

    public class PlanImpl
extends Object
implements Plan, Activity
    Process various settings related to the execution of the job. You can set scheduling related to tasks such as start time, end time, and repeat time.
    See Also:
